About Acquis

Experts to the finance and leasing industry

Our equipment insurance solutions have been delivering value to our leasing partners and their business customers for over a decade. As specialists we have a wealth of experience in leasing which helps us deliver solutions to meet our clients’ business objectives.

Read more

Our clients

Delivering results for the European leasing industry

Leading asset finance and leasing companies across Europe rely on our leasing industry expertise to enhance their asset finance offering. Working in partnership with our clients, our programmes have delivered impressive, sustainable results.

Read more

Steve Bowden

Acquis have worked collaboratively with us and continue to be a valued and trusted partner."
